      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Establishes the State-Owned Historic Properties Preservation Plan Working Group within the Department of Land and Natural Resources to ensure the preservation of state-owned historic properties and inherited lands.  Requires reports to the Legislature.  Effective 7/1/2050.  (SD1)"
    }
